## Summary
Notivize is a no-code platform for product engagement notifications that integrates with Amplitude for cohort syncing. The documentation outlines the two-part setup process: generating an API key in Notivize and configuring it in Amplitude Data, followed by instructions for syncing cohorts from Amplitude to Notivize.

